com.cloudpos.serialport

Interface SerialPortOperationResult

  • All Superinterfaces:
    OperationResult

    public interface SerialPortOperationResult
extends OperationResult
    SerialOperationResults are generated by the Serial device implementation to notify the application of the completion of a requested operation.

    The getResultCode() method inherited from OperationResult is used to retrieve the result of the operation. Constants are defined in OperationResult for that purpose.
